
NAME 

  CernVM Image Builder

DESCRIPTION

 This folder contains the scripts for the autonomous build agent in the proper
 POSIX filesystem layout.

 There are two sub-packages:

  - perl-lib  : Contains the builder plugin for iAgent
  - package   : The builder utility

INSTALLATION

 You need to install both per-lib and package packages:

 Install perl agent using the following script:

  # cd perl-lib
  # perl Makefile.PL
  # make 
  # sudo make install
